Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.57,0:00:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, everyone, we're going \Nto start Kaleido Star.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star, please \Nkeep your room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well. Do you have siblings?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nice older brothers or sisters. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.25,0:00:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or darling younger brothers or sisters?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.13,0:00:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Very soon, I'm going to be an older sister.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it a boy? Or is it a girl? \NI should be very happy, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.03,0:00:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm a little anxious. I am. I am.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.99,0:00:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dare mo sagashiteru yume wa kitto aru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dokoka ni aru {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:01:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Negai ga itsuka kanau made hitori ja nai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saigo made yareru to ittetane {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kitto tsuyogatte itanda {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.90,0:01:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Itsudatte muchabakka de zutto karamawari de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dakedo anata dake ga soba ni ita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Daremo sagashiteru yume wa kitto aru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arukidaseru {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Koko kara nanika ga hajimaru {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shinjite itai {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:02:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mada minu hikari yakusoku \Nno basho e to tsuzuite yuku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Negai ga itsuka kanau made hitori ja naisa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. But, you don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to find a room where \NI can live with my friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we've decided to create \Nour own company together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I'm sure it'll be hard, \Nbut I want to give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I don't think I'll go \Nback there for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er... Well... What should I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's why they say "Congratulations" \Non occasions like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy for you, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sound kind of weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm acting the same as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:03:02.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Amazing Family Ties."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.90,0:03:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.19,0:03:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As of today, a new life will start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A new... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should be happy. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But why do I feel this way? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to look so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will come with you, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're coming with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. So rest easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you {\i1}ever {\i0}peep into Mia or Anna's bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're going to immediately \Nbe food for Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late. You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have everything with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we find our own place,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll take you up on your offer \Nand stay with your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in my family is also \Nlooking forward to seeing you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.52,0:03:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sarah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.73,0:03:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, all you guys are finally heading out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Miss Sarah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving for training, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.28,0:03:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Training?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She left to train for singing. Didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:04:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, she looked like she \Nleft for martial arts training.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's Miss Sarah, \Nthat could be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, thanks to Ken's family, \NI was really saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandma felt relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, a newspaper \Nalready printed an article
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,saying that after Kaleido Stage's \Nowner changed, the cast quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way that I can turn \Nyoung girls out into the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you sound very manly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tease me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you worried about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Oh... No. It's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your suitcase!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before you come to my house,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is something I want \Nyou to be prepared for...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be prepared for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already spoken strictly \Nto her about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, my younger sister is especially...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a park.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. My father built it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father? Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:04:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know. And, about my younger sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Anna! It's really Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pose, pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My younger sister, Lucy, is a big Anna fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't think it's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not nice to keep \Nthem outside for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, hurry. Come inside quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben! Everyone is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, all you do is rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to get the idea \Nfor a new design of...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, move, move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, please, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father designs furniture.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so modest, have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:05:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a seat, quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Anna is sitting on our couch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ook Ook!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna is different from what I had in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this was no good either?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if posing as a \Nmonkey is too ordinary...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave your luggage here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This room is so adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This used to be a kid's room. \NSo it's kind of messy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. It's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you design this, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, if you find anything you like,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can take it with you when \Nyou find your own place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. This time hold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I still want to take \Nmore pictures of Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, take it easy until dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should find our apartment quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we should.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A kid's room... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once my father and mother's \Nreal child is born, I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been depressed for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I don't think I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did he sneak in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a bug or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry for making all that noise. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How shall I say this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to show you how sorry I feel, \Nlet me help you prepare dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Us too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:07:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our place is always noisy, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken used to jump off the bunk bed \Noften when he was a child too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He'd say that he was \Ngoing to be a Kaleido Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, that boy, since he was a child, \Nhis heart's been weak, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, it wasn't so bad that he had \Nany problems living a normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, he had a hard time giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how he feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, as his mother, I couldn't \Nlet him do what he really wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I'm nervous,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,worrying that he may say he wants to \Nappear on stage one of these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.83,0:08:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ken{\i0}! Give me my camera back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you have this, you'll \Nkeep chasing after Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with it? I'll \Nbrag about it to my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should invite your friends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is the real Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, please don't say anything unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.49,0:08:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did the same. We used \Nto fight all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I had a quarrel with \Nmy mom, it was rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At our house... I don't think we ever fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's have dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just enjoying the cool weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry my place is so noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I think it's very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone says whatever is on their \Nminds. It's like a real family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they're your adopted parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.49,0:09:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,aren't they your real family?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sure. What am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're worried about \Nsomething, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the contrary, there's \Nsomething to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother is going to have a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to have a sibling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They couldn't have a baby for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought they weren't having kids \Nbecause they were concerned about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if they were, I thought \NI'd feel so bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I feel better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:10:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When my younger sister was born, \NI remember I felt a little sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is something natural,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but both my parents devoted all \Ntheir energies to my newborn sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I used to say unreasonable \Nthings on purpose,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and gave my mother and father a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm afraid I can never \Ndo anything like that:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,having a serious fight, or \Nspeaking my mind to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid of destroying our family bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.76,0:10:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... think I can be part of \Na family if it's with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're like family, you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mia and Anna too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.69,0:10:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to make our own Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no time to be depressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First thing tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will try hard to find an apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good night, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:54.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I didn't mean it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since I'm with everyone, I \Nshould be able to keep going.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Also, I want to show my performances \Nto my mother and father.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be my friends forever too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She gets rougher and rougher with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Empress...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A penthouse with a yard...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A standalone house in the suburbs \Nmight not be a bad idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's less expensive and it looks \Nlike it's in a convenient location.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:11:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Policeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it not good?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place was robbed before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not easy to find a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not necessarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's old.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as bad as it looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rent is cheap, it's in a \Nconvenient location, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I live here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The inside is cleaner than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty big.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The view is good, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it motivates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think this place is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From here, we're going to start \Nup our own Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By all means!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.81,0:12:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I live just below,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just let me know if there's \Nanything you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:12:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it perfect?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, why don't we have \Ncoffee or something in my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In {\i1}your {\i0}room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little messy, but \Ndon't let it bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who usually cleans up this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A perfect place...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's the distinct possibility we'll \Nhave to clean Miss Kate's room too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I guess there is no \Nsuch thing as the perfect deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerry, where's the coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerry?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Mr. Policeman's name is Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too good for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares what kind of name I have?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.01,0:13:30.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew we would find a place so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we're lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy will be disappointed to lose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we leave Anna alone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's waiting in front of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father... Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.69,0:13:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.84,0:13:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since she came here all the way from \NJapan in that kind of condition,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they came here \Nto take Sora back with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After we finally found our own apartment...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You surprised me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause all of a sudden \Nyou were waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we went to your dormitory, they \Nsaid they had no idea where you went.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it took a while to find this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.44,0:14:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry. I meant to call you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, are you okay coming all the way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother insisted on coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was concerned after we talked on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I sound that bad? Weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're worried about me, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.17,0:14:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over the phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell whether you're \Ndoing all right or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way, we found an apartment today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That policeman Father met referred it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't you feel relieved?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's even a doctor \Nliving on the floor below us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Miss Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Mr. Policeman is \Nsecretly in love with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come back to Japan for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because if you've quit Kaleido Stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:14:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you'll have a hard \Ntime making a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're worried about that, \Nmy friends and I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you're going to \Ncreate your own Kaleido Stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you rest for a little while \Nin Japan, you will get new ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you do that, we don't need \Nto worry about you every day either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, can you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before long, you won't have \Ntime to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you have your own child...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why wouldn't we worry about you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd never be like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't come here to say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should also apologize. Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Midori?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear! Ken, call an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben, get a car ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Midori, be strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ambulance will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:15:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Midori! Midori!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Caesarean section?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.87,0:16:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's only seven months pregnant...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emergency situation. \NThere are no other alternatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you calm down a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that she'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I said something \Nterrible to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought that once \Nmy mother had a baby...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There would be no room for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know my mother is so \Nhappy about having a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't feel happy for her \Nfrom the bottom of my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I don't like being like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought if I went back to Japan now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my mother would sense that \Npart of me that I don't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... I said something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother was trying so hard to be a family...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:17:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I... I broke it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you worried about your mother \Nfrom the bottom of your heart right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wishing that she'll have \Nthe baby without any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that's \Nwhat family is all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you are a real family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, your \Nfamily will never fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both your mother and her \Nbaby are trying hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's cheer them on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Thank you, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mother, please hold on. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And, you too, baby... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please... Please be born safely...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm waiting for you. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother is calm. She's resting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so tiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother was only seven months pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were in an incubator like she is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, your mother and father \Nwere so worried about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they blamed themselves too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unable to hold you for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,every time they saw you in the incubator,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they used to tell you to be \Nstrong and grow up healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember very well that they \Nwere cheering for you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you told me you wanted \Nto join Kaleido Stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.07,0:18:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the first thing that came to my mind was:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:19:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If he were here, what \Nwould your father say?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.93,0:19:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much I thought about it, \NI didn't get the answer in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, perhaps, I thought he would have \Nbeen bewildered and sent you off
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while worrying about you like I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little Sora became so big,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she found what she \Nwanted to do by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your mother and I will \Nnever stop worrying about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, go see your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I scared you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you apologizing? It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said something terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was not what I really think.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:19:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:20:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I knew how anxious you were,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I said something that \Ndrove you into a corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and put you in a situation that you had \Nto say something you didn't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you near me when the baby was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you are the \Nonly big sister she has.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then you said something like \N"I'm not coming home" on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I lost my composure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told your father something selfish,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,saying that I'd go right over \Nto see you as soon as I hung up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks to that, my wish came true
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even though it was different \Nfrom what I was expecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come closer, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for growing up a healthy girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we decided to adopt you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was anxious, wondering whether \NI could be your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's the same \Nkind of anxiety you had.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you called me "Mother" \Nfor the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so happy, I secretly cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, when you're away from \Nme, I worry about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, when I think that you're \Ndoing fine and working hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I adore you so much, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.85,0:21:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have any problems, you have \Nto tell me, at any time. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.04,0:21:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.75,0:21:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you name the baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.43,0:21:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted you to name my baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.09,0:21:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said she had a healthy baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's celebrate! Celebrate! Call everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who she is talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Empress card also represents childbirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... She is adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.02,0:21:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little sister... Congratulations, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.03,0:21:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we didn't do anything extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.11,0:21:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have such a nice son.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:21:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.96,0:22:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A nice son? Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You did a good job, little sister.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will too. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.92,0:22:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will do my best here for my dream.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.52,0:22:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.55,0:22:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.30,0:22:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.42,0:22:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The baby's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.01,0:22:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yume! I want to name her Yume. "Dream."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.84,0:22:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yume...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a nice name, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.44,0:22:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.11,0:22:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... No... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yume... I hope she grows up fast.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:36.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Kaleido Star"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.26,0:22:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need to repay Sora's kindness a lot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.08,0:22:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, it's our show, a new challenge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.92,0:22:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though Miss Layla rejected it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To our surprise, Rosetta \Ncame here to help us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.22,0:22:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And a mysterious shadow dashingly \Nappeared like the wind...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is she really? Who? Who?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.47,0:22:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time on Kaleido Star, "An \NAmazing Change From Zero to Hero."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My wings are my dream and \Non towards the sky...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.89,0:23:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Boku wa koko ni iru sora to \Nmichi no aida de mukai kaze{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.54,0:23:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Soshite mae o muiteiru mou nido \Nto kanashimi ga furanai youni to{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ano kabe o koete kokomade kitanda{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.39,0:23:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nigedashitaku naru koto wa nando mo aru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dakedo kokoni irunara taishite bibitte inai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.07,0:23:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kakinaguri no uta "hajimekara yareba iisa"{\i0}
